\end{eqnarray}
have the proper dimension and are $S$-invariant. Thus, our ansatz for the fully supersymmetric actions is
\begin{eqnarray}\label{SUSYredactA}
&& S_0 = S_0^{bos}+\gamma_0 S_0^{ferm}, \\
